title: List your old summoner names in this thread you used to have
body:
Im curious, because many people I have seen changed their name, I dont seem to recognize who they were before they changed their name, nor do I remember anyone that I used to know from boards/Old GD 

let us jog our memories back 

Alright so Ill start, my old summoner names used to be, from order

-OnIy Ahri
-Ahri Mid or AFK

and now Im named as Popstar Ahri right now
